<div class="container" id="content">
  <div class="top-utilities">
    <div class="search-form">
      <form>
        <label for="product-search">Search</label>
        <input class="" type="text" placeholder="Search for any reward" id="product-search"/>
        <input class="submit search-btn" type="submit" value="Search" />
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- hero block -->

  <div class="hero-unit">
    <img src="../img/content/hero-placeholder-boost.jpg" alt="Placeholder for Landing page image"/>
    <div class="hero-content-container">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="hero-title">
          <h1>Say hello to Clubcard Boost</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-strapline">
          <p class="hero-sub-txt">The new name for Exchange and Rewards. Are you ready to boost your vouchers and make them go further?
            <span class="hero-cta">
              <span class="hero-cta-item">
              <a href="">Ready to Boost</a>
              </span>
              <span class="hero-cta-item">
              <a href="">How does it work?</a>
              </span>
            </span>
          </p>
        </div>
        <span class="hero-chevron">&nbsp;</span>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- content block -->


  <div class="component-container">
    <div class="heading-container">
      <div class="heading-container-text">
        <h2>Clubcard Boost is the new name for Exchange and Rewards</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="component-container">
    <div class="content-block">
      <div class="content-list lead">
        <p>
          Why the change? We wanted to make Exchange &amp; Rewards simpler to use and easier to understand.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <p>You can still get up to 4 times your voucher value with our Boost Partners (previously 'Clubcard Rewards').</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>You are now able to turn every £5 worth of Clubcard vouchers into £10 to spend in selected Tesco departments throughout the year (previously 'Clubcard Exchange').</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>Look out for our special seasonal events in summer and at Christmas where you can still exchange your vouchers in more departments.</p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

